      • BIO_FINGERPRINT_KEY_INVALIDATED

        public static final int BIO_FINGERPRINT_KEY_INVALIDATED
        Deprecated.
        An internal key has been invalidated by the system.
        • User has enrolled new fingerprint after the activation of BioFingerprint mode.
        • User has changed the lock screen configuration.
        Application integrator should de-activate and re-activate BioFingerprint mode.
        See Also:

      • BIO_AUTHENTICATION_BLOCKED

        public static final int BIO_AUTHENTICATION_BLOCKED
        Deprecated.
        Maximum authentication attempt reached. The sensor is blocked by the system. The user has to wait for approximately 30 seconds. On some devices, user is required to enter the pass code through the lock screen to unlock the sensor.
